OL,3,CMan jailed for arson and police
OL,4,Cassaults
OL,6,FA Carlisle man has been jailed for
OL,7,Ffive years for arson and assaulting
OL,8,Fpolice officers, in incidents last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FPaul Gillan, aged 43, was sentenced on
OL,12,FFriday 5 September at Carlisle Crown
OL,13,FCourt for arson, a public order
OL,14,Foffence and four counts of assault on
OL,15,Fan emergency worker.
OL,17,FThe offence of arson was related to an
OL,18,Fincident in the early hours of 17
OL,19,FNovember last year (2024) when Gillan
OL,20,Fset fire to a woman's car.
