OL,6,F"The consequences of his actions could
OL,7,Fhave resulted in serious injury or
OL,8,Feven death.
OL,10,F"The danger he poses to the public is
OL,11,Falso highlighted in the aggression he
OL,12,Fdisplayed towards police officers
OL,13,Fresponding to concerns regarding his
OL,14,Fbehaviour.
OL,16,F"We are pleased that Gillan has now
OL,17,Fbeen removed from society."
